OL,5, A mother is suing a building firm over 
OL,6, its failure to implement safety        
OL,7, measures which led to the death of her 
OL,8, 10-year-old son in Glasgow.            
OL,10,FShea Ryan entered a construction site  
OL,11,Fin Drumchapel with his friends through 
OL,12,Fan insecure fence in July 2020.        
OL,14,FHe told them he wanted to climb down a 
OL,15,Fmanhole but slipped on a ladder and    
OL,16,Ffell about 6.3 metres (20ft).          
OL,18,FIn April contractor RJ McLeod admitted 
OL,19,Fbreaching health and safety laws and   
OL,20,Fwas fined #800,000.                    
